txt.en: The Giants must have no Gathered Rage when defeated
Somewhere within Isengard Saruman has entrusted two of his lieutenants with rings to command the elements of fire and frost.
The giants have fallen. Challenge complete.
Find the bearers of the Rings of Fire and Frost
You must find the bearers of the Rings of Fire and Frost.
Both Dunlending giants must be defeated when they have zero Gathered Rage.
